living with us.

867
00:40:30,256 --> 00:40:30,975
That's not true.

868
00:40:32,216 --> 00:40:33,296
Don't overthink it.

869
00:40:34,376 --> 00:40:35,615
You're not the problem.

870
00:40:37,416 --> 00:40:38,816
I'm not the problem,

871
00:40:38,856 --> 00:40:40,776
