872
00:40:41,816 --> 00:40:44,256
So is it because the two children
are too naughty?

873
00:40:44,856 --> 00:40:45,535
No.

874
00:40:46,135 --> 00:40:46,936
Like I said,

875
00:40:48,495 --> 00:40:49,655
it's not your problem.

876
00:40:53,416 --> 00:40:54,135
Aunty,

877
00:40:54,455 --> 00:40:55,455
I just thought that

878
00:40:55,495 --> 00:40:56,736
